text: Nang Ngumiti ang Langit (/) is a 2019 Philippine drama television series starring Sophia Reola. The series premiered on ABS-CBN's PrimeTanghali noontime block and worldwide via The Filipino Channel from March 25 to October 18, 2019, replacing Playhouse. ==Series overview== ==Episodes== ===Season 1 (2019)=== ;Episodes notes ==References== Category:Lists of Philippine drama television series episodes
